sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard / API User)
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InitC as eval-runtime-init<br/>(Init Container)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as Evaluation Adapter<br/>(Lighteval / lm-eval / etc.)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP localhost
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking Server<br/>HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Execution (Kubernetes)

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: TokenReview Response (authenticated identity)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Resource: trustyai.opendatahub.io/evaluations:create
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: SAR Response (authorized)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (job.json + sidecar_config.json)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap created
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create Batch Job<br/>(init + sidecar + adapter containers)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created
    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (job ID + status)

    Note over InitC,S3: Init Container Phase
    InitC->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials (from Secret)
    S3-->>InitC: Test data files

    Note over Adapter,OCI: Evaluation Execution Phase
    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTP localhost (plaintext, pod-local)
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: Forward status event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token, TLS 1.2+
    EvalHub-->>Sidecar: 200 OK
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: 200 OK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>HTTP localhost
    Sidecar->>MLflow: Forward MLflow request<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    MLflow-->>Sidecar: Run created
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: Run created

    Adapter->>Sidecar: PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/uploads<br/>HTTP localhost
    Sidecar->>OCI: Push artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (challenge-response), TLS 1.2+
    OCI-->>Sidecar: Upload complete
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: Upload complete

    Note over Client,EvalHub: Flow 2: Authentication & Authorization Detail

    Client->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + X-Tenant header
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (cached 2min)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Identity (user, groups)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SAR: can user GET trustyai.opendatahub.io/evaluations<br/>in namespace from X-Tenant? (cached 5min allow / 30s deny)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Allowed
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Query storage with tenant scoping
    EvalHub-->>Client: 200 OK (filtered job list)
